      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "GM21P Mouse",
      "description": "The RGB BACKLIT GAMING MOUSE (GM21P) is designed for gamers, featuring a cool, streamlined design that enhances grip. It boasts a 12000dpi high-resolution optical sensor, with adjustable resolution via driver software. The mouse includes chromatic RGB circulation backlighting that changes with DPI settings, ensuring you always know which mode is active. Gaming sensors work on any surface, and the DPI change button allows for quick adjustments to mouse movement speed. The side forward button has a non-slip design to prevent accidental presses, improving efficiency and precision. It also features an upgraded 12000 DPI optical engine for stable and precise control, side anti-skid buttons, ergonomic design for right-handed users, support for Marco Programming with 16.8 million customizable RGB colors, a durable USB braided cable, and a 6D soft-touch switch with a matte finish for a comfortable, non-slip grip. It's a Plug & Play device, ready to use in seconds without additional software installation.",
