        "templateName": "",
        "shortDescription": "Experience the Air GW39 -- a top-tier gaming mouse that perfectly blends a lightweight design with powerful performance. Featuring the high-precision PAW3395 sensor with up to 26,000 DPI for ultimate sensitivity and accu",
        "longDescription": "Experience the Air GW39 -- a top-tier gaming mouse that perfectly blends a lightweight design with powerful performance. Featuring the high-precision PAW3395 sensor with up to 26,000 DPI for ultimate sensitivity and accurate control. The 100% Teflon feet ensure smooth and durable movement, while the stylish green transparent white dot RONO switches provide long-lasting and reliable clicks. Versatile connectivity options (2.4G wireless, Bluetooth, and USB wired) cater to all your usage needs and the RGB-lit magnetic charging dock. Specifically designed for medium to small hands, supporting both palm and claw grips for comfortable and effortless operation during extended use. Upgrade your gaming gear today, master every precise action, and elevate your gameplay with the Air GW39.\\n\\nUnleash Your Gaming Potential\\nPAW3395 sensor with 26,000 DPI and 8000Hz polling for extreme precision. Huano green-dot switches for durability. Tri-mode connection: 2.4G, Bluetooth, and USB. RGB magnetic charging dock. Designed for small to medium hands with palm and claw grip support.\\n\\nSuperior Multi-Mode Connectivity\\nSupports 2.4G wireless, Bluetooth (BT), and USB wired connection modes, ensuring a stable and efficient experience in any environment. Whether you prefer wireless freedom or wired stability, seamless switching caters to various usage scenarios.\\n\\nHighly Durable Buttons for Long-Lasting Reliability\\nThe Air GW39 features Huano switches, rated for up to 100 million clicks. Additionally, the buttons are designed with stylish green transparent white dot switches, enhancing both aesthetics and visual appeal. Whether during intense gaming sessions or everyday use, each click remains precise and reliable, ensuring long-lasting durability.\\n\\nHigh-Precision Sensor for Accurate Control\\nEquipped with the genuine PAW3395 sensor, the Air GW39 offers up to 26,000 DPI, delivering unparalleled tracking speed (650 IPS) and impressive acceleration (50g). Whether for rapid movements or precise maneuvers, the Air GW39 responds accurately, giving you a competitive edge in gaming.\\n\\nMaximum 26,000 DPI for Ultimate Sensitivity\\nThe Air GW39 boasts a maximum DPI of 26,000, ensuring ultimate sensitivity and precision across various usage scenarios. Whether it's for high-speed movements or fine adjustments, the 26,000 DPI caters to the needs of professional gamers and meticulous designers alike, delivering an unparalleled control experience.\\n\\nHigh Polling Rate for Low Latency\\nWith a high polling rate of up to 8KHz in wireless mode and 1KHz in wired mode, the Air GW39 ensures rapid transmission of commands, minimizing latency. Whether for fast-paced gaming or precise design tasks, the Air GW39 delivers smooth and uninterrupted responsiveness.\\n\\nUltra-Lightweight Design for Prolonged Comfort\\nWith dimensions of 119.5*62*40mm and weighing only 58g, the Air GW39 is specifically designed for medium to small hands, offering a comfortable grip for both palm and claw styles. Its ergonomic design reduces hand fatigue, making it ideal for extended gaming or office sessions, ensuring smooth and effortless operation.\\n\\nPower Through Your Week with Long-Lasting Battery\\nEquipped with a high-capacity 400mAh battery, the Air GW39 requires just 2 hours of charging to deliver up to 30 hours (with lights on) or 60 hours (with lights off) of enduring battery life. Reduce the hassle of frequent charging and stay focused on what matters most.\\n\\nMagnetic Charging Dock with RGB Lighting\\nWith a magnetic charging dock featuring RGB lighting, offering a convenient wireless charging experience. The stylish charging dock not only enhances aesthetics. Additionally, the built-in 400mAh battery supports rapid 2-hour charging, providing up to 20 hours of continuous usage, ensuring uninterrupted performance for extended use.\\n\\nFlexible Driver Support for Easy Setup\\nThe Air GW39 offers both web cloud drivers and local drivers, compatible with Windows 10/11 and macOS 13+. Users can easily customize DPI settings, button functions, and lighting effects, ensuring optimal mouse performance tailored to individual needs.\\n\\n100% Teflon Feet for Smooth and Durable Movement\\nEquipped with 100% Teflon feet, ensuring smooth and precise movement across various surfaces. The Teflon material is not only durable and resistant to wear but also reduces friction, enhancing the fluidity of operations. Whether for intense gaming or everyday office tasks, the 100% Teflon feet provide a long-lasting and stable sliding experience.",
