      "description": "Introducing the Meetion GW32, an ergonomic gaming mouse tailored for right-handed gamers. It features the advanced PAW3220 sensor with up to 8000 DPI and a 1000Hz polling rate, ensuring precise tracking and ultra-low latency for impeccable performance. The GW32 boasts a durable 20 million click lifespan and customizable RGB lighting, blending style with functionality. Its 700mAh battery offers remarkable longevity, providing up to 35 hours of use with lights on and an impressive 115 hours with lights off. Designed for comfort and control, the mouse includes dual scroll wheels and an ergonomic shape, making it perfect for extended gaming sessions. Multiple connectivity options---2.4G, BT1, BT2, and USB---provide versatile compatibility with various devices. Weighing just 98g (excluding cable), the GW32 is lightweight and easy to maneuver. Complete with Meetion's exclusive driver for full customization and compatible with Windows 10/11, the GW32 is the ultimate gaming companion, combining precision, style, and flexibility.",
