      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "MK005 Keyboard",
      "description": "The MK005 is a 60% mechanical gaming keyboard featuring OUTEMU blue switches for crisp sound and good feedback. Its ergonomic design caters to gamers' pursuit of hand feel and performance, enhancing operational efficiency and ensuring a longer service life. Available in classic black and white, this keyboard saves desktop space and meets the daily needs of both gamers and office professionals. It includes customizable LED backlighting with adjustable brightness and speed, full-key anti-ghosting, and 12 multimedia keys. It comes with a standard 1.8-meter USB cable.",
