      "description": "The K9520 RGB Magnetic Wrist Rest Keyboard for Gaming is a high-quality membrane keyboard designed for gamers and office professionals. It features a quiet and precise keystroke, an ergonomic design, and a surface treatment that enhances hand feel and performance. The keyboard offers customizable macro recording, RGB background lighting with adjustable brightness, 26-keys anti-ghosting, and 12 multimedia keys. It comes with a durable 1.8-meter braided USB cable. The high-intensity magnetic palm rest provides excellent support, relieving palm numbness during extended use. The volume adjustment button allows for quick and convenient control. It is plug-and-play, requiring no additional software installation.",
