    {
      "id": "prod_1775215897655w2c94w",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "HP012 Headset",
      "description": "At MEETION, we understand the importance of having the best gaming equipment to enhance your gaming experience. That's why we bring you the MEETION Gaming Headset series, designed to immerse you in a world of realistic soundscapes and crystal-clear voice chats. Our gaming headsets are built to last, with durable materials that withstand the rigors of intense gaming sessions. The advanced drivers deliver high-fidelity audio that lets you hear every detail, from the softest footsteps to the loudest explosions. With noise-canceling technology and a built-in microphone, the MEETION Gaming Headset ensures you can communicate with your team clearly and effectively. The lightweight and ultra-comfortable design allows you to wear the headset for hours without any discomfort. Whether you're gaming on a console or a PC, the MEETION Gaming Headset series has you covered. With a range of models and colors to choose from, you can find the perfect headset to match your gaming style. Join the ranks of elite gamers around the world who trust MEETION to be their ultimate gaming companion. Experience the difference today.",
      "price": 19.99,
      "originalPrice": 19.99,
