      "id": "prod_1775215897655hprym5",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BTH011 Headset",
      "description": "The new BTH011 gaming headset brings you the ultimate auditory experience! Equipped with a noise-canceling microphone, the call is clear and unobstructed, and the angle is adjustable. Triple-mode connection (2.4G wireless + Bluetooth 5.3 + wired) allows you to enjoy a variety of connection methods. 800mAh large-capacity battery, up to 25 hours of battery life, long-lasting and worry-free play. 50mm large-size driver unit, presents professional-grade game sound quality, allowing you to immerse yourself. Compatible with Type-C/USB-A dual interfaces, seamless switching between multiple platforms. The earmuffs can be rotated 90° in one direction, flexible adjustment, and comfortable fit. BTH011, born for gaming, for you!\\n\\nThree Modes for Free Connection\\nSupports three connection modes: wireless 2.4G (USB Type-C), Bluetooth 5.3, and wired, intelligent switching of multiple devices, and full-scene adaptation, allowing you to enjoy a hearty combat experience.\\n\\n30ms Smooth and Low Latency\\nWith 2.4G connection, the delay is as low as 30MS, the sound and picture are synchronized, and the accurate sound and position identification can easily control the battlefield and enjoy the pleasure of the game.\\n\\n50mm Drivers for Powerful Detailed Sound\\nThe 50mm large driver unit, which has been professionally acoustically tuned, brings a powerful shocking effect while providing more detailed restoration. You can clearly and accurately capture various sounds in the game world, bringing an immersive gaming experience.\\n\\nRotatable Noise-Canceling Microphone\\nCompatible with a variety of usage scenarios, e-sports dedicated microphone, achieve high-definition voice calls, greatly improve the game voice communication performance.\\n\\nPower-Packed Performance Battery\\n800mAh boasts a powerful and enjoy uninterrupted gaming fun. battery that provides up to 25 hours of playtime.allowing you to game endlessly. Say goodbye to frequent charging interruptions.\\n\\nPhysical Buttons for Your Precision Control\\nThe physical buttons on the left earmuff can directly control the volume and microphone in the game, and your personal preferences are determined by yourself.",
