      "id": "prod_1775215897655xpslyv",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BTH012 Headset",
      "description": "Experience the superior performance of the BTH012 multi-mode gaming headset! This headset integrates three connection modes: wireless 2.4G, Bluetooth 5.3, and wired connection to meet your needs in different scenarios. The 50mm driver unit brings professional-grade gaming sound quality, allowing you to immerse yourself in shocking sound effects. The 1200mAh large-capacity battery supports up to 45 hours of continuous use, allowing you to play without worries. The detachable microphone not only ensures clear communication, but also facilitates storage. The ergonomic design with sports mesh material and memory foam ear pads brings a comfortable and fitting wearing experience. BTH012, born for your gaming experience, makes every moment full of passion!\\n\\nThe BTH012 multi-mode gaming headset delivers immersive sound quality and comfort, featuring 2.4G, Bluetooth 5.3, and wired connections, along with a long-lasting battery and detachable microphone.\\n\\nThree Modes for Free Connection\\nBTH012 has four gaming connection modes, which can connect to multiple devices such as desktop computers, laptops, PS4, PS5, Pad, mobile phones, etc. It is compatible with multiple platforms and you can switch to play all day long!\\n\\nSeamless Audio Experience Uninterrupted by Interference\\nIn a complex environment where multiple devices coexist, audio transmission is not affected, providing a seamless listening and communication experience.\\n\\n50mm Drivers for Powerful Detailed Sound\\nThe 50mm large driver unit, which has been professionally acoustically tuned, brings a powerful shocking effect while providing more detailed restoration. You can clearly and accurately capture various sounds in the game world, bringing an immersive gaming experience.\\n\\nDetachable Noise-Canceling Microphone\\nEffectively reduce the impact of environmental noise, reduce noise during calls, and make communication smoother.At the same time, the microphone rod can be plugged in and bent, so you can store it and enjoy listening.\\n\\nErgonomic Comfort Designed for Endless Wear\\nThe representative of comfortable ergonomics, long-term wearing without pressure! The optimized ergonomic design ensures stability and comfort, allowing your ears to listen freely. The soft and breathable mesh headband, sports mesh and memory foam earmuffs fit perfectly. The headband is retractable and adjustable, and the ear shells are light and flippable, bringing an all-round comfortable experience.\\n\\nPower-Packed Performance Battery\\nBuilt-in 1200mAh battery, up to 45 hours of battery life, so you don't have to worry about battery life.\\n\\nClassic Black and White Headset\\nTwo-color options, a perfect combination of function and fashion, suitable for any occasion.",
