      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BTH014 Headset",
      "description": "Experience the ultimate in gaming audio with the BTH014 Surround Sound Wireless Gaming Headset, designed specifically for gamers seeking an immersive experience. Featuring a triple-mode connectivity option—wireless 2.4G, advanced Bluetooth 5.3, and wired connection—you can easily switch between different setups. Equipped with professional-grade 50mm drivers, this headset delivers exceptional sound quality, bringing every detail to life. The powerful 1000mAh battery ensures up to 50 hours of uninterrupted performance, perfect for those marathon gaming sessions. An adjustable noise-canceling microphone provides crystal-clear communication, making it effortless to chat with teammates or engage in voice calls. Plus, with its ergonomic design featuring a soft high-protein headband and earmuffs, the BTH014 guarantees comfort even during extended use. Choose the BTH014 for an unparalleled gaming experience!",
