      "id": "prod_1775215897656cn5fib",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "DSK20 Furniture",
      "description": "The DSK20 gaming table is a professional gaming desk with an ergonomic curved design, providing space for arms and wrists to rest comfortably during work and gaming. It features adjustable foot pads for stability and anti-tilt, ensuring the desk remains steady. The desk is constructed with thick R-Type high-quality all-metal legs and a real steel frame, making it extremely stable without additional support rods. It includes a better cable management system with two cable holes for convenient storage and manipulation. The gaming desktop has a smooth carbon fiber texture, preventing scratches and water spots. An RGB background lighting design allows switching between various lighting modes via remote control, with adjustable brightness and dynamic light speed, filling the room with a gaming atmosphere.\\n\\nExquisite Desktop:\\nThis gaming desk features a sleek carbon fiber texture surface that effectively protects against scratching and water damage. The 0.98-inch thick P2 particle board desktop can bear a large load without deformation.\\n\\nCable Organized System:\\nThe two cable holes are specially designed for players, allowing for easy desktop cleanup and organized placement of game equipment.\\n\\nSturdy R-shaped Design:\\nFeatures a powerful R-shaped design made of heavy-duty metal, providing superior support and stability.\\n\\nGaming:\\nA gaming table specially designed for gaming enthusiasts, perfect for use with gaming chairs, immersing you in the game atmosphere.\\n\\nAdjustable rubber feet:\\nThe bottom features rubber feet for better floor protection, allowing you to achieve a perfect horizontal position.\\n\\nEnvironmentally friendly materials:\\nMade of high-quality, odorless materials, with a cool black and reflective finish for the ultimate cool feeling.\\n\\nDynamic RGB Lighting:\\nOffers 7 attractive colors and 7 variable modes, switchable via remote control. Brightness and speed of dynamic lights are adjustable, enhancing the gaming atmosphere in your room.\\n\\nEasy to Assembly:\\nComes with clear and detailed instructions, numbered parts, and all necessary tools, allowing assembly to be completed within 30 minutes.",
