      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BK300 Accessories",
      "description": "Perfect Desk Accessory RGB light effect, Ambilight The Perfect Combination Of Stand And Headset. The BK300 Smart lighting towers, with RGB backlight design, allow you to manually adjust the light mode and light speed, perfectly matching your gaming keyboard and mouse. This highlights the atmosphere, immersing you in a colorful world. The ambient light is equipped with a bracket that can mount headphones, and a one-touch button turns on or off the backlight, which is convenient and quick. Powered by USB-Type C, it's plug and play, with no driver required. The headphone holder, lamp tube, and base are detachable and easy to carry. The base of the ambient light adds weight and a non-slip rubber pad for optimal stability even during intense gaming, always keeping your headset safe.",
