      "description": "The C505 4-in-1 package combination is specially designed for gaming. It includes a USB multimedia keyboard with colorful backlit and 19-key anti-ghosting. The mouse is ergonomically designed with a contour that conforms to the curvature of the palm, making it easy and comfortable to hold for long gaming sessions. Its 3200DPI high-resolution light sensor tracks high-speed data, instantly responds to opponent movements, and quickly locates targets. Side buttons allow for quick forward or backward actions, and the DPI change button adjusts mouse movement speed while indicating current settings. The headset features an ergonomic design with comfortable leather earmuffs, clear stereo sound, and a high-sensitivity microphone. The mouse pad has a smooth cloth surface for smooth operation and a non-slip bottom to prevent deformation and prolong life. The C505 package fully satisfies your gaming pursuits.",
