        "shortDescription": "The C500 4-in-1 package combo is designed specifically for gaming, offering a comprehensive set of peripherals to enhance your gaming experience. It includes a USB multimedia keyboard with colorful backlighting and 19-ke",
        "longDescription": "The C500 4-in-1 package combo is designed specifically for gaming, offering a comprehensive set of peripherals to enhance your gaming experience. It includes a USB multimedia keyboard with colorful backlighting and 19-key anti-ghosting for precise input. The ergonomically designed mouse features a contour that comfortably fits the palm, ensuring extended gaming sessions without discomfort. Its 2400DPI high-resolution optical sensor tracks high-speed data, providing instant response to opponent movements and quick target acquisition. The DPI change button allows for on-the-fly sensitivity adjustments, with visual indicators for current settings. The combo also features comfortable leather earmuffs, clear stereo sound, and a high-sensitivity microphone for the headset. A smooth cloth surface mouse pad with a non-slip, precisely locked bottom prevents deformation and prolongs life. The C500 package is a complete solution to satisfy all your gaming needs.",
