        "longDescription": "Ergonomic design for comfortable use RGB illumination for a dark atmosphere Rechargeable battery for continuous use\\n\\nFeature:\\n* Ergonomic design for comfortable use.\\n* Dual connectivity with Bluetooth 5.2+ 3.0 and 2.4G wireless (with type-c adapter).\\n* RGB illumination for a dark atmosphere.\\n* Rechargeable battery for continuous use.\\n* USB-A receivers and type-c adapter for versatile compatibility.\\n* 4 adjustable DPI levels (800-1200-1800-2400) for precise control.\\n* Dedicated forward and backward buttons for easy web navigation.\\n* Noise-reducing design for shared workspaces or quiet environments.\\n* Note: BTM010 mouse does not allow you to manually adjust the color of the light, but you can turn the light off and on by pressing the DPI for 3 seconds.\\n\\nMEASURE YOUR HAND:\\nOur ergonomic wireless mouse is designed to accommodate both large and medium-sized hands. With its vertical shape and comfortable grip, it provides a natural fit that reduces strain and fatigue, making it ideal for extended use. Whether you have large or medium-sized hands, our mouse is built to provide a comfortable and precise experience, making it the perfect choice for anyone who values comfort and precision.\\n\\nForward and Backward Button\\nWith dedicated forward and backward buttons, our wireless mouse lets you navigate the web with ease. No more fumbling around with your browser's navigation buttons.\\n\\nMute Click Design\\nEnjoy a quiet workspace with our mouse's silent click feature, allowing you to work or play without disturbing those around you.\\n\\nUSB Receiver\\nSay goodbye to messy cords and hello to seamless connectivity with our Bluetooth and 2.4G wireless mouse. The usb-a receiver is at the bottom of the mouse, the type-c adapter is inside the package and the charging cable is put together.\\n\\nWindows/Mac/Android System\\nBTM010 vertical ergonomic mouse comes with both USB-A receivers and type-c adapter, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of devices and providing you with flexibility and convenience.\\n\\nRGB Backlight Mode\\nGet in the zone with our RGB illuminated wireless mouse. Available in various colors with automatic flashing and create an immersive experience. (This mouse does not allow you to manually adjust the color of the light, but you can turn the light off and on by pressing the DPI for 3 seconds.)\\n\\nLong Battery Life\\nStay powered up and ready to go with our rechargeable wireless mouse. No more worrying about running out of batteries mid-session or having to constantly replace them.",
