      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "R545 Mouse",
      "description": "R545 wireless office mouse, exquisite and compact, easy to carry, suitable for all people. The mouse adopts a new generation of low-power energy-saving technology, which automatically sleeps when idle, which is conducive to environmental protection. Overall lightweight design, long hours of work will not feel tired. The mouse is rich in color matching, and there are 5 colors to choose from, namely: black, white, pink, cyan, blue. Comfortable to the touch, fine texture. Suitable for office, home, outdoor leisure and entertainment, etc., it can easily cope with various occasions, and the comfortable soft touch coating will make you happy for a long time and create a comfortable environment for you. The USB transmitter is plug and play and can serve you for a long time.\\n\\nPortable business\\nBeautiful appearance, comfortable grip, easy to carry!\\n\\nErgonomic design\\nDelicate and comfortable hand feeling. Keeping the wrist in a natural system, effectively relieve fatigue and free to control.\\n\\n2.4G wireless\\n2.4g wireless transmission technology, Effective working distance up to 10M.\\n\\nMatte soft-touch plastic\\nThe mouse has a pleasant matte finish that is not only comfortable to the touch but also won't slip out of your hands even after prolonged use. And if you have wet wipes nearby, the traces will be wiped off in an instant.\\n\\nEnergy efficient, Durable life\\nAutomatically sleep during leisure time, Smarter and more energy efficient\\n\\nPlug & Play\\nThe mouse works autonomously and without the need to install additional software. When connected to a computer via a USB port, you can be up and running in seconds.",
