      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BTM100R Mouse",
      "description": "The BTM100R Wireless Dual-mode Mouse integrates advanced technology with user-friendly design, featuring 2.4GHz wireless and dual Bluetooth 5.1 for stable and fast multi-device connectivity, enabling seamless device switching for efficient multitasking. With five adjustable DPI levels ranging from 800 to 3200, it caters to various needs from precision design to fast-paced gaming. The ergonomic, streamlined design and lightweight 73g body ensure comfortable use, even for extended periods, while the silent clicking enhances productivity in quiet environments. Its built-in 300mAh rechargeable battery, combined with smart power-saving technology, provides up to 60 hours of continuous use, eliminating frequent charging worries. Fully compatible with Windows, Mac, and Android systems, it performs smoothly on various surfaces, ensuring a refined and efficient user experience wherever you are. The BTM100R is not just a mouse but your ideal companion for boosting productivity and enhancing your work-life balance!",
