    {
      "id": "prod_1775215897656tqlcat",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BTM185 Mouse",
      "description": "A New Era of Wireless Dual Mode\\n\\nSmarter and More Convenient Work!\\nThe dual-mode mouse BTM185 combines 2.4GHz wireless transmission and Bluetooth 5.1, supporting up to 3 devices with one-click switching to meet the demands of efficient multitasking. It features adjustable DPI levels from 800 to 3200, adapting easily to various work scenarios. The ergonomic design provides a comfortable, natural grip, while silent left and right buttons reduce noise for an immersive working experience. Equipped with an AA battery, it offers up to 220 hours of use with an intelligent sleep mode to conserve energy. Its compact and lightweight design makes it easy to carry, perfect for office work or travel. Compatible with Mac and Windows systems, it is plug-and-play with no required drivers, ensuring a smooth and seamless experience. The BTM185 is your ultimate solution for efficient, convenient, and comfortable smart working!\\n\\nPlug and Play\\nStart a Seamless Work Experience\\nBTM185R features 2.4GHz wireless + Bluetooth 5.1, 3-device switching, 800-3200 DPI, silent buttons, 60-hour battery life, smart sleep, compact design, Mac/Windows compatibility, and plug-and-play ease!\\n\\nDual-Mode Transmission\\nBluetooth and Wireless Compatibility\\nEquipped with 2.4GHz wireless transmission and Bluetooth 5.1, this mouse is truly plug-and-play, requiring no complex setup. It supports almost all computers and ensures a stable connection, providing a clean and clutter-free workspace.\\n\\nSeamless Connectivity\\nThree Connection Modes\\nThe mouse supports up to 3 devices simultaneously, and with a one-click switch feature, you can seamlessly transition between tasks without repeated reconnections, making multitasking easier than ever.\\n\\nVersatile DPI Settings\\nTailored to Your Needs\\nFeaturing five adjustable DPI levels (800/1200/1600/2400/3200), this mouse caters to all your needs. From detailed design work to fast-paced browsing, you can switch DPI effortlessly to match your task.\\n\\nComfort in Every Grip\\nErgonomic Streamlined Design\\nThe ergonomic design fits naturally in your hand, offering a soft and anti-slip grip. It effectively reduces wrist fatigue, ensuring a pleasant experience even during long hours of work.\\n\\nSilent Clicks\\nQuiet and Non-Disturbing\\nThe left and right buttons feature a silent design, minimizing noise distractions. Whether in the office or working late at night, you can maintain a quiet, immersive workspace.\\n\\nSmart Power Saver\\nSay Goodbye to Computer Anxiety\\nEnjoy uninterrupted use with high-performance dry cell battery and smart sleep mode, automatically resting after 20 minutes of inactivity.\\n\\nUniversal Compatibility\\nEffortless Cross-Platform Work\\nCompatible with both Mac and Windows systems, this mouse is truly plug-and-play with no additional drivers required. Whether using a desktop or laptop, it delivers a smooth, hassle-free experience.\\n\\nCompact & Portable\\nUse Anywhere, Anytime\\nThis mini mouse adapts effortlessly to any environment—wood, fabric, or couch— ready to tackle any task wherever you go",
      "price": 19.99,
      "originalPrice": 19.99,
      "salePrice": 19.99,
      "image": "https://www.meetion.com/lifisher-m0/1736132047933-1/png80-t3-scale100.webp",
      "images": [
        "https://www.meetion.com/lifisher-m0/1736132047933-1/png80-t3-scale100.webp"
      ],
      "stock": 20,
      "rating": 0,
      "reviews": 0,
      "sku": "BTM185-MOUSE",
      "brand": "",
      "specs": {
        "templateId": "",
        "templateName": "",
        "shortDescription": "A New Era of Wireless Dual Mode\n\nSmarter and More Convenient Work!\nThe dual-mode mouse BTM185 combines 2.4GHz wireless transmission and Bluetooth 5.1, supporting up to 3 devices with one-click switching to meet the deman",
        "longDescription": "A New Era of Wireless Dual Mode\\n\\nSmarter and More Convenient Work!\\nThe dual-mode mouse BTM185 combines 2.4GHz wireless transmission and Bluetooth 5.1, supporting up to 3 devices with one-click switching to meet the demands of efficient multitasking. It features adjustable DPI levels from 800 to 3200, adapting easily to various work scenarios. The ergonomic design provides a comfortable, natural grip, while silent left and right buttons reduce noise for an immersive working experience. Equipped with an AA battery, it offers up to 220 hours of use with an intelligent sleep mode to conserve energy. Its compact and lightweight design makes it easy to carry, perfect for office work or travel. Compatible with Mac and Windows systems, it is plug-and-play with no required drivers, ensuring a smooth and seamless experience. The BTM185 is your ultimate solution for efficient, convenient, and comfortable smart working!\\n\\nPlug and Play\\nStart a Seamless Work Experience\\nBTM185R features 2.4GHz wireless + Bluetooth 5.1, 3-device switching, 800-3200 DPI, silent buttons, 60-hour battery life, smart sleep, compact design, Mac/Windows compatibility, and plug-and-play ease!\\n\\nDual-Mode Transmission\\nBluetooth and Wireless Compatibility\\nEquipped with 2.4GHz wireless transmission and Bluetooth 5.1, this mouse is truly plug-and-play, requiring no complex setup. It supports almost all computers and ensures a stable connection, providing a clean and clutter-free workspace.\\n\\nSeamless Connectivity\\nThree Connection Modes\\nThe mouse supports up to 3 devices simultaneously, and with a one-click switch feature, you can seamlessly transition between tasks without repeated reconnections, making multitasking easier than ever.\\n\\nVersatile DPI Settings\\nTailored to Your Needs\\nFeaturing five adjustable DPI levels (800/1200/1600/2400/3200), this mouse caters to all your needs. From detailed design work to fast-paced browsing, you can switch DPI effortlessly to match your task.\\n\\nComfort in Every Grip\\nErgonomic Streamlined Design\\nThe ergonomic design fits naturally in your hand, offering a soft and anti-slip grip. It effectively reduces wrist fatigue, ensuring a pleasant experience even during long hours of work.\\n\\nSilent Clicks\\nQuiet and Non-Disturbing\\nThe left and right buttons feature a silent design, minimizing noise distractions. Whether in the office or working late at night, you can maintain a quiet, immersive workspace.\\n\\nSmart Power Saver\\nSay Goodbye to Computer Anxiety\\nEnjoy uninterrupted use with high-performance dry cell battery and smart sleep mode, automatically resting after 20 minutes of inactivity.\\n\\nUniversal Compatibility\\nEffortless Cross-Platform Work\\nCompatible with both Mac and Windows systems, this mouse is truly plug-and-play with no additional drivers required. Whether using a desktop or laptop, it delivers a smooth, hassle-free experience.\\n\\nCompact & Portable\\nUse Anywhere, Anytime\\nThis mini mouse adapts effortlessly to any environment—wood, fabric, or couch— ready to tackle any task wherever you go",
        "attributes": {
          "brand": "",
          "model": "MT-BTM185",
          "color": "Black"
        },
        "importMeta": {
          "source": "Thunderbit",
          "sourceFile": "Thunderbit_7b6256_20260402_200404.csv"
