      "description": "The AK100 USB standard wired keyboard features a waterproof design with several drainage holes at the bottom. If liquids are accidentally spilled, simply shake the keyboard gently, and the liquid will drain out, allowing you to continue using it after wiping it clean. Its ergonomic design enhances operation efficiency and ensures a longer service life. The comfortable mute buttons provide a quiet environment, whether you're in an office, library, or working late at night. Suitable for various occasions, this keyboard offers a comfortable soft-touch coating for extended use. The USB interface is plug-and-play, requiring no additional software installation, making it ready to use in seconds.",
