      "title": "C2000 Combo",
      "description": "Introducing the MEETION C2000 Wireless Keyboard and Mouse Combo, designed for multi-device use across Windows/Mac, laptops, desktops, iPads, and phones. This combo features Bluetooth 5.2 & Wireless 2.4G dual mode for versatile connectivity. The C2000 keyboard offers precise key stability and a whisper-quiet typing experience, while the mouse ensures smooth, responsive tracking with five adjustable DPI settings (1200 to 3800). The keyboard includes dual kickstands for adjustable typing angles (4° and 7° inclines) for ergonomic comfort. Both devices automatically enter sleep mode to conserve energy and feature a built-in 300mAh battery with a TYPE-C charging port for fast and efficient power.",
