    {
      "id": "prod_177521589765623tz01",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "C100 Combo",
      "description": "C100 wired keyboard and mouse set adopts ergonomic design, and the character surface adopts UV printing process, which can meet the needs of business office, greatly improve the operation efficiency, and ensure a longer service life. The mouse DPI is 1000, which can meet the needs of business office. Whether it is in a quiet office, studying in the library, or working late at night, it will create a comfortable environment for you. Suitable for office, home, outdoor leisure and entertainment, etc., it can easily cope with various occasions, and the comfortable and soft touch coating will make you happy for a long time. The USB interface is plug and play and can serve you for a long time.\\n\\nErgonomic Design\\nThe ergonomic keyboard helps you keep your hands and wrists in a more natural position when typing.\\n\\nABS Plastic Shell\\nThe mouse is designed with ABS environmental protection material, which is environmentally friendly and durable.\\n\\nWaterproof design\\nThe keyboard is waterproof, you can continue to use it when the keyboard is accidentally splashed with water, drinks and other liquids during use.\\n\\nMute button design\\nThe keyboard keys are silently designed, whether in a quiet office, Studying in the library or working late at night will create a comfortable keystroke environment for you.\\n\\nMatte soft-touch plastic\\nThe mouse has a pleasant matte finish that is not only comfortable to the touch but also won't slip out of your hands even after prolonged use. And if you have wet wipes nearby, the traces will be wiped off in an instant.\\n\\nPlug & Play\\nThe keyboard and mouse works autonomously and without the need to install additional software. When connected to a computer via a USB port, you can be up and running in seconds.",
