      "description": "⛱️【High-Performance UV Umbrella】Baytion folding umbrella features a premium vinyl that effectively blocks UV and sunlight, providing multi-band sun protection for your skin. Enjoy outdoor activities without worry!\\n👌【One-Handed Auto Operation】Baytion automatic folding umbrella features a one-click open and close mechanism. Paired with a self-lubricating thermoplastic resin middle rod, it allows for smooth operation, making it easy to use with one hand, perfect for when your other hand is full.\\n💪【Windproof & Sturdy Design】Baytion compact folding umbrella is designed with 12 reliable ribs and a 3+2 combination structure, 60 high-strength fiberglass frames combined with high-density impact fabric for strong wind resistance, ensuring it remains intact even in strong gusts.\\n💦【Water-Resistant & Quick-Dry】The innovative water-resistant fabric of the Baytion umbrella guarantees no leakage during rain, while the lotus-leaf-shaped canopy allows for easy water shedding, keeping your belongings dry when folding it up.\\n🏕️【Compact & Portable for Travel】Baytion folding umbrella is engineered with a waterproof, sweat-resistant ABS matte handle and dual nylon elastic bands. Its compact design allows it to easily fit into your bag, making it an essential companion for all your travels. Met Any Questions⁉️ Please Feel Free to Contact Us( click the store name, then \"ask a question\") or email us at Support@Baytion.com.",
