      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "PUMA mens 5 Pack Performance Boxer Briefs Boxer Briefs",
      "description": "BOXER BRIEF 5-PACK: The essential 5-Pack Active Stretch Boxer Brief from PUMA is engineered for working out or just being on the go. An ergonomic design keeps these boxer briefs in place and on high performance. And yes, we've gathered this favorite boxer brief into a 5-pack to ensure you always have a wear-it-wash-it rotation at hand.\\nBUILT FOR PERFORMANCE: We created these PUMA boxer briefs with quick-dry, moisture wicking fabric, so you can experience cool comfort no matter what you're up to. Soft stretch fabric moves with you, so feel free to lunge, leap, reach, lounge—make your move and these favorite boxer briefs are right there with you.\\nGREAT FIT AND FEEL: Regular fit boxer brief from PUMA is designed to go the distance with comfort in mind. A soft, non-constricting waistband with PUMA logo creates that perfect intersection of style and comfort. Flatlock seams offer a high-performance wear without chafing. Available in sizes: S, M, L, XL.\\nPERFORMANCE MATERIAL: With 90% polyester and 10% spandex, you know you've got easy wear that's engineered to repel water and stay dry. And, wait, one more easy: our care instructions. Machine wash warm, do not bleach, tumble low dry at a low temperature, and wash with similar colors. Don't bother with dry cleaning or ironing. These boxer briefs are designed to make life easy.\\nGO FOR THE PACK: The essential 5-Pack Active Stretch Boxer Brief from PUMA is an excellent choice for high-performance activity and all-day comfort. They're sure to become your new fave boxer briefs, which is precisely why we recommend a 5-pack strategy. You'll always have a wear-it-wash-it rotation at hand.",
