      "description": "CALVIN KLEIN Trunk 3p Men, Black/Black/Black, S\\n\\nCalvin Klein underpants impress with their high quality and optimal fit. Made of cotton stretch, they feel like a second skin and give every man the highest level of comfort. No pinching, pecking or scratching. In addition, the typical Calvin Klein waistband with logo also looks great, should the shirt slip up. Thanks to great brand quality, the underpants retain their shape and colour even after frequent washing. Calvin Klein underwear is available in a practical pack of 3, so you no longer have to miss out on your favourite boxer shorts.\\n\\nProvocative Modern. Sensual. Symbolic.\\n\\nThe product has the following features:\\n\\nMaterial: 95% cotton, 5% elastane.\\nWithout fly.\\nElasticated waistband with Calvin Klein logo.\\nLow rise.\\nFit: regular.\\nCare instructions: Machine washable at 30°C, tumble dry at low temperature.\\n\\nFounded in 1968 by Calvin Klein, the global lifestyle brand of the same name still represents advanced ideas. Calvin Klein exudes minimalist aesthetics and wants to enthuse and inspire its audience. With this intention, the brand uses impressive design models and provocative images to appeal to all the senses. Calvin Klein has been part of the PVH Corp since 2003, one of the largest clothing companies in the world.",
