          "Special Features": "Breathable\nNon-slip grips\nLow cut\nStretchy material\nPull tabs\nClosed-toe fully cover design\nSweat resistant\nOdor resistant",
          "About This Item": "Breathable Low Cut Anti Skid for Kids\\nCOTTON-RICH COTTON offering all day comfort, breathability and softness to baby`s foot. Stretchy material provides a good fit to grow with your child. Medium thickness makes these baby anti-skid socks suitable for all seasons\\nPULL TABS behind the ankle helps the mom to put on and take off the socks very easily, the elastic ribbed cuffs prevent the socks from falling off, the non-slip grippers on the base offers good protection at stopping slips for your baby\\nCLOSED-TOE FULLY COVER DESIGN protects sensitive skin from dirt and helps keep the entire surface area of feet free from germ exposure. Good percent of cotton provides good sweat and Odour resistant for your little one\\nINCLUDES:Package comes with 12 pairs anti-slip baby ankle socks in 12 design",
