          "Product Dimensions": "12.1 x 5.2 x 29.6 cm",
          "Special Features": "Removes harmful pollutants, bacteria, and solid impurities, including chlorine, pesticides, pharmaceuticals, and dirt; neutralizes odors; reverses damage to hair, skin, and nails; easy to install and replace; comes with a 2-year warranty",
          "About This Item": "Multi-stage shower filtration system with proprietary tested and SGS & Eurofins certified filters reduces chlorine, heavy metals, and chemical pollutants to help improve water quality for healthier hair and skin.\\nAdvanced multi-stage health promoting filters reduce chlorine, pesticides, pharmaceuticals, dirt, and odors while helping to reverse damage from hard, chemical-filled water on hair, skin, and nails.\\nIonic shower filters designed to help minimize the effects of chlorinated water on skin and hair, promoting softer hair and soothed skin with regular use.\\nEasy installation with no plumber or tools required. Fits any standard shower hose and can be installed in minutes. Replace the filter cartridge every 70-100 showers to maintain filtration performance.\\nProduced by blu Intelligent Health Solutions with a 2-year warranty. Customer service team available to address questions or concerns. Customer satisfaction is our priority.",
