      "description": "Pamper your hair & skin. Infused with a luxurious blend of vitamin C, milk powder, glycerin, and trehalose that works their magic to promote soft, silky hair and healthy, hydrated skin.\\nPowerful filter captures even the most stubborn particles like pipe rust & other sediments. Vitamin C acts as a double agent, neutralizing chlorine and other harsh chemicals while leaving your skin and hair feeling revitalized.\\nSpa-like aromatherapy in the comfort of your home. The Be-Vita vitamin shower filter is available in a selection of mild but refreshing and relaxing scents, turning your daily shower into a luxurious spa-like ritual.\\nMade & accredited in Korea. Trust the Korean dedication to flawless details! Crafted with premium materials and top-notch ingredients, our filter elevates your shower to new heights. Discover a touch of K-beauty in every refreshing drop.\\nEasy Installation. Upgrade your shower in a snap, and with low maintenance (lasts up to 2-3 months), your spa-like oasis will last! Don't settle for the hard water blues - embrace the filtered revolution! Your skin and hair will thank you.",
