      "description": "【Healthy Material, No Odor】This 5 gallon water dispenser is made of emerging high-density plastic, food-grade silicone hose, which meets health standards and has no plastic odor.\\n【Suitable For A Variety Of Buckets】This water dispenser is suitable for 2 gallon, 3 gallon, 4 gallon and 5 gallon buckets with a neck of 2.16 inches. You don't need to pry open the lid, just press it directly to start using.\\n【Fast Pumping, Low Noise】This water dispenser for 5 gallon bottle has a built-in 4W powerful power pump, This water pump dispenser has faster pumping speed and less noise than ordinary water pumps. This water pump has a built-in 1200mah large-capacity battery, a USB charging interface, and can be recharged repeatedly.\\n【Double Buttons, Easy To Use】This water dispenser for 5 gallon bottle has 2 pumping modes, press the power button once to pump water continuously, and press the button again to stop pumping, or automatically stop after pumping continuously to 1.2L; press the 600ml button once, it can pump 600ml quantitatively and automatically stop pumping.\\n【Quality Assurance, Worry-Free After-Sale】If you encounter any installation or quality issues within 3 months, please contact us and we will provide you with a satisfactory solution.\\nPlease recharge the battery first when you receive the Water Pump for 5 Gallon Bottle. If you stop pumping water or the red light flashes, the remaining 30% of the battery will be used. At this time, it can be fully charged with the USB interface for 3-4 hours. A full charge can be used for 30-40 days or a 4-8 5-gallon kettle.This water pump for travel, camping, parties, kitchen, living room. Very convenient to carry. This product is not suitable for pumping boiled water.",
