      "description": "VERY HIGH ADHESION PERFORMANCE: The strongest mounting tape of the range delivers a superior, permanent bond intended for indoor extreme use. It is the only mounting tape working on plastics including hard plastics like PP and PE. It is also ideal on metal, painted surfaces and wood\\nHOLDS UP TO 7 KG: This double-sided mounting tape can support up to 7 kg (1kg/20cm), making it ideal for invisible hold and repair of transparent decorative objects on glass windows or acrylic objects\\nWEATHER RESISTANT: Designed to withstand harsh weather conditions, this durable double-sided tape remains effective in extreme temperatures ranging from -20°C to 80°C, ensuring durability in any climate. Ideal for indoor repairs and mounting\\nADVANCED 3M TECHNOLOGY: Featuring 100% adhesive with 3M Advanced Technology, this double sided tape provides a reliable and long-lasting hold. Ideal for quick and easy mounting solutions\\nEASY TO USE: No tools or drilling needed for the application of this double-sided 3M mounting tape. Ideal for quick and easy mounting solutions\\nAPPLICATION GUIDE: Ensure surface is flat, smooth, and can to hold mounted objects. Entire tape surface must adhere completely to both sides. Application temperature 10° C - 40° C. Clean the surface with alcohol and let dry. Apply the tape. Push firmly for 60 seconds\\nWARNING: Do not hang in areas where injury might occur if mounted object were to fall. This product has a permanent adhesive and may cause damage if removed. Do not use on wallpaper or delicate surfaces\\nIn 2025 Scotch Brand celebrates its 100 Year anniversary of bringing your ideas to life. Let's create, fix and do more together for the next 100 years!",
