      "description": "【100W USB C Cable】: UGREEN USB C to USB C cable supports PD fast charge up to 100W 20V/5A (max), 15V/3A, 12V/3A, 9V/3A, 5V/3A with USB-C Power Delivery adapters such as PD 18W/30W/45W/60W/61W/87W. It also supports Huawei FCP, Qualcomm QC 3.0 and Xiaomi Fast Charge protocol. It only takes 112 mins to fully recharge MacBook Pro 15\", as fast as the original charger cable.\\n【Universal Compatibility】This USB C to USB C cable match all PD USB C Charger and compatible with all usb c devices phone laptop camera like iPhone 17 / Air / Pro / Pro Max, iPhone 15/16/16 Plus/16 Pro/16 Pro Max, Samsung Galaxy S25/S25 Ultra/ S24 Ultra S24, Note, iPad Air, Mini, Pro, Macbook Pro, Air, Huawei, Microsoft, Dell, etc.\\n【Durable & Rugged】: UGREEN 5A USB C Cable offers an outstanding high-quality product using compact and reliable aluminum alloy shell and nylon braided cable. Not only ensure the long-term durability but also flexible enough to be wrapped up and put in a bag. Specifically, it features with the reinforced connector on both ends, 10,000+ bending test to achieve a high bending strength and good toughness.\\n【Secure & Reliable】: This USB Type C quick charge cable also build-in over-current / over-temperature / short-circuit protection and multi-layer shielding with 56Ω pull-up resistor inside, provide you the safe and stable power supply. The best option for a cost-effective fast charging and data syncing USB C to USB C cable for daily use.\\n【Rapid Data Sync】: Offers transfer speed up to 480Mbps (USB 2.0) for you to move content like 1GB movies, music, document or an entire photo library in 30 seconds.【Not support video output.】What You Get:1* 3M 100W usb c to c charging cable, 1*user manual, 24-month warranty, 24-hour customer service, lifetime technical support.",
