      "description": "【SAFE AND GREEN MATERIAL】:These wall mending agents are made of high quality resin and wall glue. The green ingredients are not only waterproof and non-corrosive, but also formaldehyde-free and non-toxic. Safe for kids, pets, elderly and chemically sensitive individuals. Great solution for your wall problems at home.\\n【QUICK DRYING】: Our wall repair pastes can be completely dry in 4 hours (Depending on the weather conditions). With the strong adhesive, it's not easy to fall off. Quick and professional solution for damaged walls, without losing calcimine.\\n【EFFECTIVE REPAIR】: This safe wall repairing ointment is not only quick and convenient. But also waterproof and mouldproof, making the wall smoother and more resistant to water. No need to pay big money, these drywall repair putties are enough to solve your wall problems effectively. Economical and environment-friendly.\\n【EASY TO USE】Everything you need for wall mending are all in the package, the sandpaper, quick-drying patch, scrapers and nozzles. The wall paint repair kit is very easy to use. Just extrude and scrape to repair holes and cracks quickly, use the scraper to scrape the repair cream until smooth. That's all. Better wear gloves while applying this cream.\\n【WIDELY USED】: This wall crack repair cream is perfect for repairing wall graffiti, stain, cracked walls, peeling walls and pinholes. Can easily solve wall damage problems in home, school and offices. Perfect for small repair projects.",
