      "title": "Heatsistence Filtered Shower Head with Handheld, High Pressure 5 Spray Mode Showerhead with Filters,Showerhead with ON/OFF Switch and Shower Bracket for Hard Water",
      "description": "✅Purify the water: Health is the thing we value most. Our handheld shower head features a with a powerful multi-stage filtration system, featuring various filtering beads mineral stone balls that effectively purify and filter your shower water.howerhead has a quadruple 15-stage powerful filtration layer. It effectively removes impurities and residual chlorine, heavy metals (lead, mercury, nickel, chromium) and other harmful substances from the water. Enjoy your shower and improves your skin and scalp environment. Improves your health\\n✅Thumb-Press Mode Shower Head: Heatsistence hand held shower head boasts a user-friendly design, featuring a single easy switch that allows seamless toggling between different modes with just your thumb, providing convenience and ease of operation. This handheld shower head features 5 spray modes, including power rain, gentle mist, intense massage, one-touch water stop feature and more, catering to your various showering needs,The one-touch water stop feature allows for quick shut-off in emergencies, enhancing safety\\n✅High pressure &Water saving: Heatsistence large handheld spray features a unique internal structure and pressure boosting technology, delivering a dense and powerful water flow that ensures comprehensive coverage for a rain-like experience, even with low water pressure. It envelops your body completely, providing a soothing shower that helps release stress and tension\\n✅ABS environmental material: This advanced filter shower head with chrome plated durable ABS environment-friendly materials, and the exterior is made of multi-layer baking paint to make it anti-corrosion, rust proof and resistant. You can use this shower head with filters for hard water to shampoo your hair, shower, bathing your kids, wash your dog, and even use the filtering shower head to flush the toilet as much as you want, either men, women, or kids to unwind after a hard day with a relaxing rain shower\\n✅Easy to Assemble: No Plumber Needed. The hand held shower head that attach to shower is easy to install. Universal G1/2\" threads quickly connect to any standard shower arm in minutes",
