      "title": "SOJITAS 78Ft Weather Stripping for Doors and Windows, Insulation Tape, Sealing Gaskets Windproof Sealing Strips, Insulating Cold, Heat, Dust, Noise and Insect",
      "description": "【LENGTH &VALUE PACK】Includes 2 rolls of EPDM weather stripping that can be split into single strips. With a total length of 24 meters (79 ft), this kit seals gaps of 4-6mm and covers up to 5 standard doors or 7 windows - perfect for whole-home insulation projects\\n【ALL-WETHER DEFENDER】Engineered with industrial-grade EPDM rubber for superior durability and a smooth finish. Waterproof design blocks drafts, reduces noise by up to 60%, and creates an insect-proof barrier - ideal for Canada's extreme seasons\\n【EASY INTSTALLATION】 1.Peel 2. Stick 3. Done! Featuring heavy-duty adhesive backing for instant application. Custom-cut lengths with scissors and install in under 2 minutes per window/door - no tools or DIY experience required\\n【STRONG ADHESION】- The glue is strong. The gasket is made of thick rubber and it pays strongly on the outer door which without influences closing and opening.Opt to put it on the outside, side gaskets, including the bottom of the door without getting to drag and lock\\n【CUSTEOMER SUPPORT】Backed by a 12-months replacement warranty and 24/7 Canadian-friendly support via Amazon Messages. We resolve all inquiries within 12 hours - your satisfaction is legally guaranteed",
