      "description": "😊【Gloves Disposable Latex Free, Powder Free】The skin-friendly nitrile-vinyl gloves are very comfortable to wear. Different from the rubber gloves, these household nitrile-vinyl gloves are latex free and powder free. Protecting your hands for cleaning, cooking, resin, painting, personal treatment, etc.\\n😊【Great Fit & Touch Sensitivity】 These single-use gloves fit your hands well with the ambidextrous and beaded cuffs design, they can be put on and off easily and quickly. You can touch your phone at any time when you wear these latex free gloves Small / Medium / Large. The thickness of gloves' fingertip is 5.51 mil, so you can hold things without worrying its slip.\\n😊【High-Quality Pure-Nitrile Disposable Gloves】Our blue kitchen gloves are made of high-quality nitrile materials, which are easy to be wear on and off. These food prep gloves are more safer than vinyl gloves and plastic gloves. The Fingertips thickness: 6 mil, Palm thickness: 4 mil, Wrist thickness: 3 mil.\\n😊【Widely Use】Nitrile disposable glove can be used for garden, kitchen, bathroom cleaning, food prep, dishwashing, painting, art resin, making nails, tattoo, pet care, daily treatment, shopping, etc. It is the best choice for household and industry. There are three sizes of these gloves: S, M, L, you can choose the suitable size according to the size of your hands.\\n😊【Sizes & Packaging】Our single-use gloves come by 100 pcs in a dispenser box, and 10 boxes in a case (1000 gloves bulk). These ambidextrous gloves are in Extra Small, small, medium, Large and Extra large sizes, suitable for men and women.",
