    {
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "MOMENT 10 Pack Microfiber Cleaning Cloth Reusable and Washable Rags Kitchen Household Cleaning Towels for Dishes, Glass, Counters - Multi-Color (30 x 30cm)",
      "description": "✅Premium Quality: Our Cleaning towels are made from high quality natural materials and no harmful chemicals and synthetic materials are added, safe for you and your family. Large Size 30 x 30cm Microfiber Cleaning Cloths are made of Premium 80% Polyester + 20% Cotton. Effectively cleans either dry or with liquid cleaners for streak-free and lint-free results.\\n✅Multi-Purpose: These multi-purpose towels are ideal for cleaning. Every household requires a set of exceptionally durable cleaning towels for housekeeping. Our microfiber cleaning cloth can be used on dry or damp surfaces. It is most commonly used as a kitchen cloth for utensils, appliances, table tops, and more. It can also be used to clean any furniture and tiny things, as well as vehicles, equipment, and workplace.\\n✅Reusable& Soft: Our Bar towels are Soft, highly absorbent, brief, but also Well-designed. Ultra soft microfiber & lint free & scratch free non-abrasive cleaning towels will not scratch coatings, paint or other surfaces. Machine washable and reusable cloths for car wash interior and exterior cleaning and dusting, long fibers trap dirt and dust, safely cleaning surfaces such as windows, mirrors, wheels, dashboard, control panels, upholstery, vinyl, metal, plastic and more.\\n✅Durable: Microfiber rags are ideal for washing, drying, and detailing in all your cleaning projects. Use them around the kitchen, cleaning spills, grease, grime, oil, and removes dirt from tools, paint brushes, and auto parts instruments to its durability. Microfiber Cleaning towels will perfectly dry without streaking.\\n✅Care Instructions: Machine washable, air dry for best results (or tumble dry low). Do not use bleach. Fresh look after wash. Great value for your money.",
      "price": 13.89,
