      "title": "Since New 12 Pieces White Long Thin Candles for Weddings, Parties, Birthdays | Long Lasting, All Season, Dripless Dinner Sticks",
      "description": "【 Beautiful & Elegant Design】: Add a warm ambience to your home with these elegantly crafted Ivory Tapered Candles. Their Classic look compliments any design and decor and adds warmth, positive energy and harmony to all your special events.\\n【 Unscented and Dripless】A Dripless candle is an ideal blend of hard wax and a perfectly sized wick. But for a dripless candle to remain dripless, burning conditions must be ideal. The candles are made from natural wax and with cotton wick. Our smokeless candles design, quality, burn time and versatility are the things you will love. Due to friction between the candles there could be marks on the candles which can be removed by wiping with a wet tissue.\\n【 Romantic Touch】: Spice up the romance with a candlelit dinner with your loved one. With a universal fit, they fit most candlesticks and candelabras, perfect for indoor and outdoor use.\\n【Table and Ceremonial Light】: 8-piece candle boxes equip you for any occasion, whether it be a wedding or celebration and more. Illuminate the aisle which the bride walks down to her wedding canopy with our elegant candle. Place a candle on each restaurant table to create a pleasant ambiance for your customers. The clean, elegant and perfectly tapered shape, makes them perfect for church prayers, and other religious rituals as well.\\n【Ideal Gift for your Loved Ones】: It is an ideal gift for many occasions such, Wedding, House Warming, Birthdays, Christmas, New Year, Mother's Day, Father's Day and many other occasions.",
