      "title": "Acanva Cooling Bed Pillows for Sleeping, Luxury Hotel Quality 3D Microfiber Filling with Breathable Cover for Side Back and Stomach Sleepers, Reduces Neck Pain, Standard (Pack of 2), Black 2 Count",
      "description": "Cooling Bed Pillows for Sleeping: The bed pillow cover is made of premium cotton polyester to stay soft, breathable, and dry. They are perfect for those who sweat easily or prefer a cool pillow to sleep with. Piping along the edge creates a neatly tailored look.\\nFluffy & Supportive: Filled with 100% microfiber similar to down which makes the pillows supportive and cozy. Whether you prefer soft or firm pillows, our comfortable pillows are for you. Enough filling makes pillows extremely fluffy. Our 2 pack bed pillows provide a great balance of supple softness and plump firmness.\\nComfort & Luxury at Home: With our bed pillows never go flat, no matter what kind of sleeping positions you prefer, including side and back sleepers, you can always get experience five-star hotel luxury and cozy at home every night.\\nPackaging Design: The bed pillows are vacuum packed and rolled in a PE bag for shipping purposes. We suggest removing the vacuum bag, shaking it a few times to make it fluffy and putting them under sun bathing a few hours regularly for healthier use.\\nPerfect Size: There are three sizes available, standard pillows 20x26 2/4pack, queen pillows 20x30 2/4 pack, king pillows 20x36 2/4 pack. The medium firm pillows down alternative filled is an ideal gift choice for your family and friends on Father's Day, Mother's Day, Birthday, Christmas, New Year, Housewarming or Back to School.",
