      "description": "🏠 Perfect Fit: These microfiber mop refills are designed for the Vileda mop and bucket spin mop and bucket, ensuring a seamless fit and optimal cleaning performance. Compatible with Vileda spin mop Easywring Bucket.\\n🏠 For All Hard Surfaces: Our mop head replacement compatible with Vileda features a super soft microfiber mop that effectively cleans dirt and grime from all hard surfaces, including finished hardwood, laminate, ceramic tile, granite, vinyl, and linoleum. Ideal for those looking for a dust mop for hardwood floors.\\n🏠 Washable & Reusable: These Vileda mop refills are machine washable and can be reused multiple times, making them an eco-friendly and cost-effective mop head replacement Vileda users can rely on. Keep extra mop pads handy for continuous cleaning!\\n🏠 Wet & Dry Use: Our spin mop replacement head works for both wet and dry cleaning. Use it wet for deep cleaning floors and mops and buckets for floor cleaning, or dry for dusting surfaces. This pack is designed to last one year, with a mop head replacement recommended every three months.\\n🏠 Efficient Cleaning & Design: The Vileda mop head features a triangle-shaped design, perfect for reaching corners and tight spaces. It effectively removes dirt, grime, and over 99% of bacteria using just water. Ideal for Vileda mop handle users looking for a complete cleaning solution!",
