    {
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "Huggies Extra Care Newborn Baby Diapers, Size 1 (Up to 5 kg), Twin Jumbo Pack, 128 Diapers",
      "description": "Huggies Extra Care Newborn Diapers in size 1 keep your baby dry, comfortable, and protected all through the day. These premium Huggies diapers are specially designed for newborn babies weighing up to 5 kg and are gentle enough to be used the day after birth. Dermatologist approved and crafted with gentle skin care in mind, these diapers offer exceptional comfort and protection for your newborn. The unique soft pillows in these nappies are designed to absorb liquids in seconds, keeping your baby dry and ensuring comfort at all times. No more wetness against the skin, just softness and protection at every touch. These diapers feature a special waistband pocket that effectively prevents leakage and protects your baby, ensuring they stay dry and comfortable, day and night. With the innovative wetness indicator, you can easily tell when it's time for a diaper change, as it changes color when wet, providing a signal that helps you keep your baby's skin fresh and clean. The nappies are made with a porous material that promotes airflow, reducing the risk of irritation and keeping your little one's skin healthy and happy. Huggies Extra Care Newborn disposable diapers are easy to pack and portable, making them an essential addition to your baby's diaper bag or baby care kit. Huggies has been committed to keeping babies' skin clean, healthy, and soft since 1968, with innovations in infant care that have helped generations of toddlers. With Huggies Extra Care Newborn Diapers, you can trust you've chosen the best for your precious bundle of joy. Discover our full range of Huggies baby items such as wet wipes, diapers in all sizes, and swim nappies for little swimmers. Huggies is always there for every stage of your baby’s development, offering protection you can trust.",
