      "description": "LUXURIOUS LOTION WITH ALOE VERA AND VITAMIN E FOR FRESH AND CALM SKIN: The Ultimate Comfort Pants Diapers with Aloe Vera and Vitamin E Lotion create a protective moisture barrier to keep your little one's skin well-soothed.\\nCOTTONY SOFT FIT FOR UP TO 100% LEAKAGE PROTECTION: Pampers Ultimate Comfort Pants Diapers feature a cottony soft fit that feels gentle against your baby's skin. And the stretchy belt cues perfectly adapt to your baby's movements\\nDOUBLE LEAK GUARDS AND SOFTER BELT: With double leak guards and a softer belt\\nDOUBLE LEAK GUARDS AND SOFTER BELT: With double leak guards and a softer belt\\nNEW BACK SHEET DESIGNS: The diaper's back sheet with charming new designs not only inspires joy but also acts as an additional layer to help keep wetness away.",
