      "title": "Jump Rope, Tangle-Free Rapid Speed Jumping Rope Cable with Ball Bearings for Women, Men, and Kids, Adjustable Steel Jump Rope Workout with Foam Handles for Fitness, Home Exercise & Slim Body",
      "description": "Durable & Adjustable Rope: This jump rope is made of steel wires coated with strong PVC material, ensuring durability even after long exercise sessions. Its adjustable length design allows customization for all users, from kids to adults.\\n\\nJump Fast, Jump Easily: Built with high-quality ball bearings, the skipping rope provides comfortable and fast jumps while preventing tangles, ensuring safety and convenience.\\n\\nErgonomic Foam Handles: The handles are designed for safety and comfort, covered with soft sponges for a comfortable grip. Non-slip and moisture-wicking features keep palms dry, making every exercise comfortable and safe.\\n\\nGet Fitness Anytime & Anywhere: Suitable for women, men, kids, adults, beginners, or experienced individuals, this jump rope can be used anytime, anywhere. It's an easy and efficient way to strengthen the body, lose weight, and increase stamina.\\n\\nPortable & Easy to Carry: This fitness jump rope is highly portable. Easily put it in your pocket and use it for workouts whenever needed.",
