      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "Sportneer Pull Up Bar: Strength Training Chin up Bar without Screws - Adjustable 75-94cm Width Locking Mechanism Pull-up Bar for Doorway - Max Load 200kg for Home Gym Upper Body Workout Non-slip",
      "description": "Note: Before purchasing, please make sure that the size of your door frame is 29.5in-37in (75cm-94cm). This Chin up Bar is not suitable for door frame widths outside this range.Not suitable for glass door frames, carved door frames, hollow wooden door frames. The pull up bar cannot be installed if the door frame has small cracks, or the wall where the door frame is installed has foam filling, etc\\nPlease read the instructions carefully before installing!!!The width of the door frame must be wider than the width of the anti-slip pads at both ends of the pull up bar!The connection between the door frame and the anti-slip pad must be a completely horizontal surface, not a curved surface.Make sure the extension on both sides is the same length during installation.\\nNote: To ensure safety and compliance, the manual specifies a maximum load of 135kg. Testing shows the product can withstand up to 337.5kg of instantaneous load, meeting the 2.5x safety factor requirement. However, the product's capacity also depends on the usage environment. Users should strictly adhere to the 135kg limit specified in the manual and not exceed it under any circumstances. Verify the marked rotation direction; reversing it may cause locking!\\n【No Drilling, No Traces】: The Sportneer pull up bar uses innovative fixative technology to hold the bar in place without the need for drilling. It is supported by 2 enlarged 6.5\"x1.8\" PVC mats to ensure enough friction for sustained use. The base and bar are connected by 4 metal fixed points that ensure the PVC mat is pressed outward if the bar slips from the base, which provides a fall-proof design for the user. The heavier the load, the more sturdy it is.\\n【Easy-peasy Installation】: The installation is quite easy. Guided by detailed instructions and video, plus 5 arrow directions on the surface and spirit levels on both ends to make your installation smooth. All you have to do is extend it to the comfortable length and height and you are good to go! Please make sure your doorway or wall is strong enough for installation. Ceramic tiles, glass, or non-solid structures are not ideal surfaces to install the fitness bar.\\n【Upgraded Mechanic Lock System】: Safety is a big deal at Sportneer, which is why we ensure the safe use of this push-up bar for users of all ages, from teens to elders. It comes with an exclusive, new 360° rotatable dual gear lock on both ends to protect the bar from loosening. This Sportneer doorway exercise bar has passed a series of research and development testing and is certified safer and stronger than other similar equipment.\\n【Integrated, Extensible Structure】: This hallway pull-up bar is different from most 2-section foam bars on the market. It comes with an ultra long, integrated anti-slip cotton handlebar that supports a flexible grip. It is sweat-resistant, odorless, and wear-proof. Simply twist the bar to adjust it to any size within 29.5\"~37\" (74.9cm~94cm) to get the ideal dimension for your workout like pull-ups, sit-ups, push-ups, stretching and more!\\n【Heavy Duty Construction】: Our Pull Up Bar is designed to support weights of up to 440lb/200kg with ease, thanks to the combination of a 2mm outer steel pipe and a 1.5mm inner steel pipe. This bar is built to last for years without deformation or breakage, making it a reliable and durable addition to your home gym. The longer the use distance of the horizontal bar, the smaller the load.",
      "price": 159.99,
      "originalPrice": 159.99,
      "salePrice": 159.99,
      "image": "https://images-eu.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61gFT3yR0FL._AC_UL300_SR300",
      "images": [
