    {
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "Sparnod Fitness STH-3002 Home Use Walking Pad & Treadmill | Compact, Ultra-Slim, Ready to Use | Shock Absorption | LED Display | Manual Incline | 100 Kg Capacity",
      "description": "🏡 Compact & Space-Saving Design -- Ultra-slim treadmill easily fits under a bed or sofa, perfect for small spaces like apartments and offices.\\n🔌 Ready to Use -- No assembly required; just plug in and start walking for a hassle-free fitness experience.\\n⚡ Powerful & Quiet Motor -- 2.5 HP DC motor ensures a smooth, low-noise operation for home workouts.\\n🚶 Adjustable Speed & Incline -- Walk at your preferred pace with a 1-6 km/h speed range and 2-level manual incline for added intensity.\\n🦵 Joint-Friendly Shock Absorption -- Deck shock absorption system minimizes impact on joints for a comfortable walking experience.\\n📊 Smart LED Display -- Track your progress with real-time updates on time, distance, speed, and calories burned.\\n⚖️ Max User Weight: 100Kg -- The max user weight of the machine should be at least 20 kg more than the person's weight as impact weight increases while running.\\n🔄 Easy to Move & Store -- Built-in wheels for effortless portability; lightweight yet sturdy design supports home and office use.",
      "price": 359,
      "originalPrice": 359,
