      "description": "【Super Bright】: The powerful XPG2 LED generates a beam of up to 1300lux, illuminating as far as 150m. This headlamp boasts an impressive 22-hour run time on a low setting, exceeding 98% of similar products on the market. Note that batteries are not included in the package.\\n【6 Lighting Modes】: There are 6 lighting modes to s6 Lighting Modes - There are 6 lighting modes to suit your different needs, including spot light (high/low), flood light (high/low), and red light (stay on/flash). You can also choose a combination of spot light and flood light.\\n【45° Tilt Adjustable】: The ergonomic 45° adjustable angle allows you to adjust the headlamp to the angle you need, without straining or craning your neck. It will be tightly fixed to avoid shaking and sliding when running. Make it your top choice for camping, running, and hiking.\\n【Comfortable to Wear】: With its removable, washable, and elastic headband, this head lamp is comfortable for both adults and kids to wear, and can even fit hard hats or helmets. Weighing only 55g (without batteries), it's the perfect LED headlamp for long-distance runners and outdoor adventurers.\\n【Water Resistant and Durable】: This rugged headlamp is protected against splashing or spraying water from any angle, and can withstand rain, cold, heat, and even drops on the ground. You no longer need to worry about using it for any outdoor activities.",
