          "About This Item": "Resistance Bands: Exercise bands will help you effectively achieve full body extension and enhance exercise in legs, hip,waist,arms and back etc's perfect for Yoga, Pilates, stretch training,losing weight,physical therapy and recovery, increase flexibility.\\nDurable and Elastic: Made from premium latex material,the exercise bands are environment friendly,non toxic with long lasting durability,elasticity and soft feeling. Elastic fitness bands are resistant to wear and tear, and are robust enough.\\n5 Colors 5 Levels: Our resistance bands include five colors representing five tensile force, easy for you to quickly identify the level you want. Whether you are a professional or a beginner, the fitness bands can fully meet your needs.\\nStrength & Flexibility Trainer:These fitness bands provide a safe and effective workout that allows you better control muscle tension in multiple directions and can be used to strengthen almost every muscle and joint,it's Ideal for improving flexibility,posture and core strength.\\nLightweight and Portable:With a supplied carrying pouch,the resistance bands are easy to carry and you can exercise anywhere at any time's perfect for working out at your home,office,gym,outdoors or even when you are on travel.",
          "Date First Available": "10/20/22",
