    {
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "PROIRON Resistance Bands Set 14 Pieces Anti-Snap Resistance Band Exercise with Handles, Door Anchor, Ankle Straps, Training Manual and Carrying Bag",
      "description": "【5 color-coded resistance bands, from very light to ultra-heavy】Resistance bands can be used individually or in combination, the load can be changed by the length of the handle. Free storage bags included for easy storage and transportation.\\n【Safety first】High-quality polyester yarn outside, more than 50 latex threads inside thus the tension is more even and safer than a single latex resistance band.\\n【More durable】The middle part of the resistance band is equipped with a protective cover to prevent the middle resistance band from being dirty during use and effectively preventing damage caused by friction between the resistance bands and the floor.\\n【Your mini gym】In contrast to conventional fitness equipment, the resistance bands set has more than 100 different training movements that are suitable for increasing muscles, muscle building and whole-body training. Whether functional training, physical training or comprehensive training - the training tubes are always an ideal training tool.\\n【Lifetime warranty】If your resistance bands are broken, please contact us immediately to replace them with new ones. We will respond as soon as possible within 24 hours and send you new products on the same day at the earliest. At PROIRON, your satisfaction is not an option, but a guarantee.",
      "price": 42.75,
