      "description": "【6% Manual Incline】This walking pad treadmill comes with a 6% manual incline, engineered to mimic uphill walking or running. Unlike flat-surface workouts, this feature helps increase calorie expenditure and engages more muscle groups for a comprehensive exercise experience.\\n【4 Vibration Modes】Walking pad Treadmill features 4 adjustable vibration modes from gentle to intense. These vibration mode can be used pre-workout to stimulate and activate muscles, or post-workout to relax muscle\\n【3.0HP Quiet Motor】Engineered with a robust 3.0HP servo motor, this walking pad delivers smooth, consistent power and supports users up to 150 kg. It offers a speed range of 0.5-12 km/h(both remote control and Sperax app can control) and operates with low noise, making it ideal for home offices and apartments.\\n【Fully installed & Easy Move】Treadmill arrives fully assembled and ready to use right out of the box. Additionally, built-in transport wheels make moving and storing it effortless, helping you save valuable space in your home\\n【LED Display & Portable】Featuring an LED display and Sperax app, this portable treadmill provides real-time feedback on key metrics like time, speed, distance, and steps. Its compact, foldable design ensures easy storage in tight spaces, such as under a bed or sofa.",
