      "description": "Recovery: Train, sleep and recover with confidence thanks to precise heart rate, fatigue and recovery monitoring. If you wear the Helio Strap together with a Amazfit smartwatch, both devices work together with the Zepp app to capture continuous data - whether you wear both or only one of the devices.\\nEasy to use: From the moment you wake up after a night of rest, your BioCharge score adapts based on your daily workouts, activities and stress levels.\\n100% SATISFACTION GUARANTEE: Get accurate heart rate data during training and stay informed throughout the day with continuous monitoring of heart rate, blood oxygen, stress and sleep -- enabled by Amazfits BioTracker technology.\\nOptions for strength and horological try: Track precise repetitions, sets and break times in the gym. The exclusive HYROX race mode provides specially tailored support for race preparation.\\n2.5 Speed & Easy to use: Use sport-specific tracking and performance analysis including VO₂ max, training load, effect and recovery time -- all via the Zepp app.\\nEasy to use: Sync, analyse and optimise everything from nutrition to recovery in one place. Get AI-powered insights to help you improve on a daily basis.\\nINTEGRATORY DRIVE PLATFORM: Sync your Zepp app data with Strava, TrainingPeaks, adidas Running and komoot to simplify your fitness ecosystem.\\nUp to 10 days: Enjoy longer time between charges. The Helio Strap delivers long-lasting performance that supports your training and recovery -- day and night.",
