      "description": "Powerful and Efficient: The electric air pump boasts a powerful motor capable of both inflating and deflating various items quickly. With a rated power of 50W and a pressure of 0.7 PSI (5000 Pa), it ensures high performance and efficiency, saving you time and effort\\nVersatile Nozzle Options: This air pump comes with three different nozzle sizes (S, M, L), allowing you to easily inflate or deflate a wide range of inflatables, including air mattresses, pool floats, inflatable furniture, and more. The nozzles lock securely in place to prevent air leakage during use\\nDual Power Supply: The pump includes both a car power adapter and a home power adapter, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use. Whether you're at home or on a camping trip, you can conveniently inflate or deflate your inflatables without any hassle\\nPortable and Lightweight: Designed with portability in mind, this electric air pump is compact and lightweight (12 x 11 x 11cm), making it easy to carry and store. Its travel-friendly size allows you to take it anywhere you go, ensuring you always have a reliable pump on hand\\nUser-Friendly Design: Featuring a unique sound insulation design with high-quality metal impellers and an advanced wheel structure, the pump operates quietly. The long 1m/1.8m power cord provides ample reach, and the simple switch mechanism makes inflating and deflating quick and easy, ensuring a hassle-free experience",
