          "Product URL": "https://www.amazon.ae/Walking-Treadmill-Incline-Foldable-Capacity/dp/B0FWK77SV7/ref=zg_bs_g_sports-goods_d_sccl_18/000-0000000-0000000?psc=1",
          "Product Image": "https://images-eu.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/71SRnQckOyL._AC_UL300_SR300",
          "Price (AED)": "499.99",
          "Rating (Max 5)": "4.3",
          "Number of Ratings": "649",
          "Brand": "CURSOR FITNESS",
          "Material": "Alloy Steel",
          "Color": "15% Black",
          "Product Dimensions": "115D x 56W x 103H centimeters",
          "Special Features": "Handle\nLightweight",
          "About This Item": "Versatile Incline Treadmill for Home Fitness: Enhance your workout intensity with our walking pad treadmill, featuring an 15% manual incline that simulates uphill training. This 3-in-1 machine combines walking, light running, and incline exercise in one compact unit. It's a space-saving all-in-one home fitness solution with a robust 136kg weight capacity.\\nPowerful 2.5HP Motor with 15% Incline: Engineered with a robust 2.5HP motor, our treadmill delivers consistent and quiet performance across 1-10km/h speed ranges. The 15% manual incline adds intensity to your walking or light running sessions, mimicking uphill training without requiring extra space.\\nSecure Walking Pad with Adjustable Handlebar: Experience enhanced stability and support during your workouts. Designed with a 136kg weight capacity for user safety, it features a 6-layer non-slip running belt (35.8\"×15.2\") and an advanced shock absorption system to minimize joint impact. Operates quietly under 45DB, making it ideal for homes and apartments.\\nLED Display with Remote Control Convenience : Track your fitness progress seamlessly with the bright LED display showing speed, distance, time, and calories. Control your walking pad experience through the included remote control, allowing convenient adjustments without interrupting your workout rhythm. The remote enhances your exercise efficiency and convenience.\\nSpace-Saving Foldable Design with Transport Wheels: This portable treadmill is designed for easy storage. It folds compactly to slide under a bed or sofa. The integrated front transport wheels allow you to move it effortlessly, saving significant space compared to traditional treadmills. An ideal compact fitness solution for small apartments and home offices.",
          "Date First Available": "03/01/23",
