    {
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "LEVOIT Smart Air Purifier with Plasma for Home Bedroom, H13 HEPA Filter with Air Quality Sensor, Removes 99.97% Pollen Allergies Dust Odours, Alexa Enabled with Quiet Auto Mode, Core300S Pro",
      "description": "Active and passive purification combines technologies. Plasma Pro technology generates both positive and negative ions, which bind to pollutants and help neutralize particulate matter, odorous gases, bacteria, viruses, aerosols, and volatile organic compounds (VOCs).\\nReal-time Air Quality Monitoring Core 300S Pro use a laser dust sensor with higher accuracy, faster detection, and a larger particle size range (≥0.3um). Your concerned PM2.5 will be displayed on our smart VeSync APP and the air quality is prompted by the colour change of the Indicator Colour on the purifier panel\\nEfficient 3-Stage Filter System The first defence primary filter can filter dust, pet fur, lint; The second defence H13 HEPA filter trap 99.97% of airborne particles such as pollen, pet dander. The last defence activated carbon stage can effectively filter out unpleasant smoke and odours. 3-Stage defences protect your each breathes\\nDouble purification with fan and ion types, sterilization rate of over 99.99% ① The \"Plasma Pro\" released into the air reaches the entire room, not only neutralizing dirt floating in the air, but also cleaning odors and bacteria attached to walls and clothes. ② The evolved unique HEPASmart technology removes more than 99.97% of ultra-fine particles such as dust, pollen, PM2.5, and viruses up to 0.1 μm. Furthermore, the sterilization rate reaches 99.99%, so it protects the health of your family in every way\\nSuitable for Room Size Up to 108 m² The effective purifier area of Core 300S Pro can meet the needs of most families. Purify once in one hour, and the purification area can reach 108m²/458ft² each time. 360 air intake design, all-around air purification. It's perfect for bedrooms, living rooms, and offices\\nFree Your Hands and Enjoy Your Fresh Air Simply ask Alexa or Google Assistant to control the air purifier when your hands are full. The free VeSync app also allows you to customize some preset like schedules. Not sure which gear to use Click the automatic mode, let Core 300S Pro automatically select the most needed mode according to your air quality.Ultra-Quiet Sleep Mode No light, no noise, just air purification! Sleep soundly while the air purifier works as quietly as 22dB for light sleepers.",
      "price": 569.99,
      "originalPrice": 569.99,
      "salePrice": 569.99,
