      "title": "Lint Roller Remover Hair Kit- Extra Sticky Reusable Lint Remover with 360 Sheets(6 Rollers+2 Upgraded Handles)-Fluff Brush for Clothes/Furniture/Bed/Car/Dog Cat Hair/Carpet/Dust",
      "description": "📍【Extra-Sticky Lint Roller】Lint remover with professional strength adhesive can remove fluff, debris, dirt, etc. faster without leaving anything unwanted. with it, keep the sofa, sheets and carpets clean all day.The set contains 2 reusable plastic handles, 6 extra refills, and each paper core has 60 pages, totaling 360 stickers（𝗡𝗼𝘁𝗲: 2 handles in the roller. If there are no handles, kindly please contact us to replace）\\n🔎【Comprehensive & Damage-Free Cleaning】Baytion lint roller is made of premium PP and professional strength adhesive tape, and the handle is made of solid plastic, which is durable without any signs of wear. When the paper roll is installed on the handle, it can easily rotate 360 °, It is good at cleaning hard-to-reach places, such as debris and hair in a small space. Because of the high-quality adhesive, it is non-toxic and tasteless, and will not damage the fabric and leave traces.\\n✍【Ergonomically Upgrade Handle】The ergonomically designed handle is not only comfortable to hold, but also small in size, light weight. You will be able to easily pick up pet hair, dust, food crumbs or other things from the surface, so as to keep the furniture and home clean and tidy, And the tail of the handle is provided with a round hole, which is convenient for hanging and saves space.\\n🛠【Easy to Use & Peeling】Lint roller adhesive paper adopts spiral winding and pre-cutting design, Compared with other papers, ours is easier to peel off. You find six extra refills in the set, which ensures that you don't have to worry about changing new refills frequently. Replacement is easy, just pull out the used refill from the drum and insert a new refill into the drum.\\n🏠【Use It Anywhere】The lint remover for clothes can effectively remove pet hair, fluff, food residue, dust, dirt and dandruff, and is suitable for different types of places, such as bedroom sheets, clothes, furniture, sofas, car seats, carpets, If you have problems and need help. please feel free to contact us( click the store name, then \"ask a question\") or email us at support@baytion.design.",
