      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max 512GB (6.7-inch) Natural Titanium - Dual eSIM (US Version) – A17 Pro Chip, 48MP Camera, Titanium Design, 5G, iOS 17",
      "description": "Experience ultimate performance and luxury with the Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max. Featuring a stunning 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR display with ProMotion, powerful A17 Pro chip, advanced 48MP camera system, and premium titanium design — built for speed, photography, and everyday excellence.\n\nThe Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max is Apple’s most powerful and advanced smartphone, designed with cutting-edge technology and premium craftsmanship.\n\nBuilt with a titanium frame and textured matte glass back, it delivers a lightweight yet ultra-durable feel. The 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR display offers incredible brightness, sharpness, and smooth scrolling with ProMotion technology, along with the convenience of an Always-On display.\n\nPowered by the A17 Pro chip with a 6-core GPU, this device delivers unmatched performance for gaming, multitasking, and professional-level applications.\n\nThe Pro camera system takes mobile photography to the next level with:\n\n48MP Main Camera\nUltra Wide Lens\nTelephoto Lens\nUp to 10x optical zoom range\nHigh-resolution 24MP & 48MP photos\nAdvanced portrait mode with Focus & Depth Control\n\nThe Dynamic Island introduces a new interactive way to stay connected with alerts and activities, while the customizable Action Button gives you quick access to your favorite features.\n\nFor safety, it includes:\n\nEmergency SOS via satellite\nCrash Detection\nRoadside Assistance via satellite\n\nWith USB-C connectivity (USB 3 support), you get up to 20x faster data transfer speeds.\n\nEnjoy up to 29 hours of video playback, secure unlocking with Face ID, and ultra-fast 5G connectivity for seamless performance anywhere.\n\nKey Features:\n- 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR Display with ProMotion\n- Always-On Display\n- Premium Titanium Design\n- A17 Pro Chip with 6-core GPU\n- Dynamic Island Interface\n- Customizable Action Button\n- Pro Camera System (48MP + Ultra Wide + Telephoto)\n- Up to 10x Optical Zoom Range\n- 24MP & 48MP High-Resolution Photos\n- Next-Gen Portrait Mode with Depth Control\n- Emergency SOS via Satellite\n- Crash Detection & Roadside Assistance\n- Up to 29 Hours Video Playback\n- USB-C with USB 3 Fast Transfer\n- Face ID Security\n- 5G Connectivity\n- iOS 17 Operating System",
      "price": 2850,
      "originalPrice": 3200,
      "salePrice": 2850,
